name: Welcome to the real world
description:
Now you can't close your eyes and think of the good world.
The world has come a long way
until you meet a human
I believe this world will remain forever.
But are we the ones who can survive?
Welcome to the real world
The world that we created
...
Our good and evil work at full strength.
Let's see how it ends.
Or maybe this is just the beginning?
by l3tanq
